Dulcie Cooper https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dulcie_Cooper 0 Dulcie Cooper (3 November 1903 – 3 September 1981), briefly known as Dulcy Cooper, was an Australian-born American stage actress who also performed in silent movies and later in television.
